        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;This resolution calls on elected officials, faith leaders, and civil society leaders to condemn and counter antisemitism.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The resolution also (1) urges that all possible steps be taken to ensure the safety and security of Jewish American communities, and (2) calls on the Executive Branch and civic leaders to identify and educate the public on the contributions of the Jewish American community.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
